      <title>温和多风天气缓解欧洲天然气价格下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/european-gas-prices-slip-as-mild-windy-weather-brings-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于温和多风的天气有助于防止库存加速消耗，欧洲天然气价格连续第五天下跌。]]></description>
